node.text: Delighted to be part of @GoZwift Fun is Fast 2021 campaign. During this year's @letourdefrance, don't just watch the pros race across the 3 weeks at home, get on Zwift and take part in the series with rides and workouts inspired by @geraintthomas86 and @annavdbreggen and myself that prove that #FunIsFast.
